Description: Water permeability of the RBC membrane
Electrodiffusional anion permeabilities (Cl-, HCO3-, gluconate-, SCN-) (Goldmanian)
Electrodiffusional H+ permeability (Goldmanian) to simulate protonophore additions
ionophore-induced Ca and Mg fluxes to simulate effect of divalent cation ionophore additions
pI, Isoelectric point of Hb A at 0 oC, to allow simulation of oxy-deoxy transitions
